copper wire, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 28lbs. weight of pin points, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 2 drawers, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18410201-name-564" type="victimName">
