                        <interp inst="t18410201-name-567" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM PENNY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a police-inspector. I was on duty when the prisoner was brought to the station.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Were you surprised at seeing him? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—Ihad been three or four times at the prisoner's house.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
